			<p align="center" class="blurb"><em>2009 Hugo Award Winner </em>for Best Fanzine </p>
			  <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="content" -->
			<p class="header">Submissions </p>
			<p class=content><em>Electric Velocipede</em> is currently closed to submissions. </p>
			<p class=header>Getting Around the Site </p>
			<p class=content>There are links on the left for editor John Klima's Twitter and Facebook pages. He tends to talk about mostly <em>Electric Velocipede</em> related things there, so if you like the magazine, check them out.  Occasionally he'll talk about libraries, too. There is an '<a href="htm/art.htm">art</a>' link that showcases all the covers from past issues, as well as some fun things that we do here. All the individual back issue pages now have cover art at the top of their pages.</p>
			<p class=content>The catalog/shopping section lists items that are for sale from editor John Klima. Current issues and subscriptions are handled by <a href="http://www.nightshadebooks.com">Night Shade Books</a>. Click on the '<a href="htm/shop_sales.htm">sales</a>' link to find special deals.</p>
			<p class=content>There is a selection of fiction online in the '<a href="htm/free_fiction.htm">free fiction</a>' link. The '<a href="htm/issues.htm">back issues</a>' link will give you excerpts of all the stories, as well as most of the poetry that's been featured in the magazine. </p>
			<p class=content>We're running some ads in the amazing magazine Coilhouse, so hello! to visitors from there! Take a look around! They're doing some amazing stuff at Coilhouse, all sorts of things to make us green with hate and red with jealousy (or is it the other way around?).</p>
			<p class=header>T-shirts</p>
			<p class=content>We have some amazing t-shirts that we made. On the <a href="htm/tshirts.htm">t-shirts page</a>, you can see the amazing <a href="http://www.sandrawickham.com" target="_blank">Sandra Wickham</a> wearing a shirt. We have both men's and women's sizes from S to XXL. At $20 each, they're quite a steal! </p>
